## Summary
This documentation page explains Amplitude's Lifecycle Chart, a tool that categorizes active users into new, current, and returning segments, while also tracking dormant users to help product teams understand user base growth over time. The chart offers three views (Growth, Dormant, and Pulse) to analyze user engagement patterns and retention trends based on critical events.

